title: Test
summary: This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Share of respondents, with a total of 4 data points.
Overall Share of respondents has decreased over the Year.
Share of respondents is slightly increasing from 9_PM_-_2_AM to 4-9_PM, and lastly roughly constant from 4-9_PM to 7-11_AM.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 9_PM_-_2_AM and 4-9_PM.
Max Share of respondents about 48.0 was recorded at Year 4-9_PM
Min Share of respondents about 10.0 was recorded at Year 7-11_AM
This line chart has an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Share of respondents, with a total of 4 data points. The chart has 2 significant trends.
The longest trend is slightly decreasing which exists from 9_PM_-_2_AM to 7-11_AM.
Differently, the next significant trend is slightly increasing which exists from 7-11_AM to 7-11_AM.
